<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>解脱 - 标签 - 无名老人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/</link><description>无名老人的文章</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 22:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>学佛人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%BD%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%A7%8B%E9%80%94/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 22:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%AD%A6%E4%BD%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%A7%8B%E9%80%94/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="学佛人心行之始途"&gt;&lt;span&gt;学佛人心行之始途&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%ad%a6%e4%bd%9b%e4%ba%ba%e5%bf%83%e8%a1%8c%e4%b9%8b%e5%a7%8b%e9%80%94" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：十二因缘、无明、破无明、发愿、大乘菩提心、出离、解脱、佛知见、清净心、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　学佛人随顺佛的开示，在真修实行中实证漏尽通，就能以正观体察到十二因缘的来龙去脉，深知众生的“老死”是以“生”为本，若能离“生”就无“老死”；说到“生”也不从天生，绝不是说生就生，亦不是无缘由就生，而是从因缘所生，即三界众生造业由业而生；三界众生所“有”业从何而生？三“有”业从见取、欲取、禁戒取、我语取之四“取”生；四“取”从“爱”（爱憎）而生；“爱”从“受”而生；“受”从“触”而生；“触”从“六入”（六识）而生；“六入”从“名色”的分别生；“名色”从“八识”而生；“识”从“行”的起动而生；“行”从“无明”而生。所以“无明”若灭，“行”即灭；“行”灭，“识”即灭；“识”灭，“名色”（心物分别）即灭；“名色”灭，“六入”即灭；“六入”灭，“触”即灭；“触”灭，“受”即灭；“受”灭，“爱”即灭；“爱”灭，“四取”即灭；“四取”灭，“三界有业”即灭；“有”灭，“生”即灭；“生”灭，诸苦即灭。可见，修行人了生死的关键就是破“无明”。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>四圣谛</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A3%E8%B0%9B%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 18:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%9B%9B%E5%9C%A3%E8%B0%9B%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E4%B9%89/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="四圣谛真实义"&gt;&lt;span&gt;四圣谛真实义&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%a3%e8%b0%9b%e7%9c%9f%e5%ae%9e%e4%b9%89" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：四圣谛、苦集灭道、大般涅槃经、声闻缘觉、菩萨、外道、有漏无漏、解脱、佛子、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　佛对五比丘说：你们五位，苦应知，集应断，灭应证，道应修，苦集灭道是真实不虚的，你们若不解苦集灭道四圣谛的真实甚深义，那么与解脱是无缘的。四圣谛乃学佛人入佛门的共法，也是解脱的基础大法。不解此义者，皆是佛在《大般涅槃经》中所说“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;一切众生皆依非真邪伪之法&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”的盲修瞎练者，何以故？著相著魔故。今依经义，详述四圣谛之真实甚深义。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>十八不共法</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%B1%E6%B3%95-%E5%94%AF%E4%BD%9B%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B7/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 16:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%B1%E6%B3%95-%E5%94%AF%E4%BD%9B%E7%8B%AC%E5%85%B7/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="十八不共法唯佛独具"&gt;&lt;span&gt;十八不共法，唯佛独具&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%8d%81%e5%85%ab%e4%b8%8d%e5%85%b1%e6%b3%95%e5%94%af%e4%bd%9b%e7%8b%ac%e5%85%b7" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：十八不共法、佛、功德、六度万行、智慧、解脱、大乘、方等经、佛子、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　十八不共法，唯佛独具，乃如来超越一切声闻、缘觉、菩萨之殊胜功德。此十八法，从身口意三业无失，至智慧知三世无碍，彰显佛果究竟圆满之境界。学佛人若能实发救拔一切众生心，方能持心待悟，契入此不共法之真谛。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>能观心者</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="能观心者究竟解脱"&gt;&lt;span&gt;能观心者，究竟解脱&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%83%bd%e8%a7%82%e5%bf%83%e8%80%85%e7%a9%b6%e7%ab%9f%e8%a7%a3%e8%84%b1" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：观心、解脱、本心、佛性、大乘、法华经、大般涅槃经、圆觉经、于相离相、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　能观心者，究竟解脱，不能观者，究竟沉沦。何以故？经曰“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;不识本心，学法无益&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”故。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>